    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly way to get around? This vehicle is priced to move and ready for its next chapter! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical attention and TLC to get it back to its best, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a handy owner or someone looking for the lowest entry price on the market. It's an honest car with plenty of potential for the right person!",
      "price": 4500.0,
