      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original, untouched character. Meticulously inspected to ensure mechanical and cosmetic perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire an investment-grade asset. Experience the pinnacle of luxury and performance in a vehicle that defies its age.",
      "price": 46500.0,
